description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Welcome to Italy: Classical Pilates' from the channel Christie Wang.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement. The The Zen Flow vibe means Grounding, intentional, breath-centered, unhurried. This is especially good for When you need balance, mindfulness, and release..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Move through this classical pilates with Christie as she welcomes you to the beautiful view of Tuscany. ...
